com.twilio4j.twism

Interface EnqueueParameters


  • public interface EnqueueParameters

    Twilio will pass the following parameters in addition to the standard TwiML Voice request parameters with its request to the 'action' URL parameter of Enqueue.

    Author:
    broc.seib@gentomi.com

    • Method Detail

      • getQueueResult

        QueueResult getQueueResult()
        Returns:
        The final result of the enqueued call. See QueueResult for details.

      • getQueueSid

        java.lang.String getQueueSid()
        Returns:
        The SID of the queue. This is only available if the call was actually enqueued.

      • getQueueTime

        int getQueueTime()
        Returns:
        The time the call spent in the queue. This is only available if the call was actually enqueued.
